window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>For the first time ever, the entire Fire Mage Chronicles have been made available in one convenient volume. </b></p> <p>From mild-mannered history professor to ultimate bad-ass, John will overcome his inner demons as he fights to defeat the evil Lich King.</p> <p>Fortunately, he's not alone. Assisted by powerful female warriors and mages, John will traverse the length and breadth of Zamina. </p> <p>Between laying down the law on lizard men and traveling to far-off islands in search of an all-powerful magical orb, John will hone his sword-fighting and fire-casting abilities. </p>"; 
